name: chinask
description:
#8 “under.stage” collection explores the underground events environment of northeastern Brazil.

rapper "diomedes chinask" finishing the day of recording his street video, opening the show for "racionais mc's", the biggest brazilian rap group.

diomedes chinask is an icon of the new generation of brazilian music, his lyrics range from social protest to party music, love songs to brazilian funk, a poet without borders.

recife - pernambuco - brazil - 2016
